General.Name: AVJennings Limited
General.Description: AVJennings Limited engages in the development of residential properties in Australia. It is involved in the development and sale of land, new homes and townhomes, and apartments. The company was founded in 1932 and is based in Hawthorn, Australia. AVJennings Limited is a subsidiary of SC Global Developments Pte. Ltd.
